best = {'tp': 100, 'fp': 20, 'miss': 10, 'fp_rate': 0.0003, 'tp_rate': 0.93,

    0.96, 'miss_rate': 1e-05}

    'miss_rate': 0.00011}
best, change = fle.change_best(1000, best, stats1)

best, change = fle.change_best(1000, best, stats2)
